A '''massacre''' took place in [[Ettam]], a small town on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ralltiir/Legends|Ralltiir]], during the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] rule of the world.

==History==
The massacre was one of many violent events on Ralltiir, during the conflict between the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] and the local rebel cells. It was perpetrated by [[Imperial Army/Legends|Imperial Army]] [[Commander/Legends|Commander]] [[Akobi]], who, while [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] fighters blocked his communications, ordered an attack on what he thought to be a rebel ammunition depot.<ref name="Empire 13" />

Instead, his [[TIE/sa tactical bomber/Legends|bombers]], following the coordinates he gave them, destroyed a medcenter packed with innocent civilians. The incident was downplayed by the Galactic Empire, and [[Akobi]] was made a hero. The massacre occurred a few days before the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of]] [[Yavin Prime/Legends|Yavin]] and the destruction of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|first Death Star]].<ref name="Empire 13" />

